data.description: Wake up to colorful sunrises over the sparkling waters of Lake Michigan.  Perhaps catch a view of the cruise ship anchored off your shoreline.  Peacefully private front yard with a cedar tree lined, blacktopped driveway leading to a two car garage.  Double glass doors welcome you inside the home where nearly a full wall of windows let the watercolor views inside.  Convenient open kitchen and living area, full bath with granite countertop and double sinks along with large bedroom and den complete the first floor.  Upstairs you will find another full bath, bedroom with mini deck overlooking the lake, and another bedroom or office area.  A large deck surrounds two sides of the home making for a relaxing place to enjoy the sounds of the waves.
